      • prepare

        public MemStoreSize prepare()
        This is not thread safe. The caller should have a lock on the region or the store. If necessary, the lock can be added with the patch provided in HBASE-10087
        指定者:
        prepare 在接口中 StoreFlushContext
        返回:
        The size of snapshot to flush

      • flushCache

        public void flushCache(MonitoredTask status)
                throws IOException
        从接口复制的说明: StoreFlushContext
        Flush the cache (create the new store file) A length operation which doesn't require locking out any function of the store.
        指定者:
        flushCache 在接口中 StoreFlushContext
        抛出:
        IOException - in case the flush fails

      • commit

        public boolean commit(MonitoredTask status)
               throws IOException
        从接口复制的说明: StoreFlushContext
        Commit the flush - add the store file to the store and clear the memstore snapshot. Requires pausing scans. A very short operation
        指定者:
        commit 在接口中 StoreFlushContext
        返回:
        whether compaction is required
        抛出:
        IOException

      • getCommittedFiles

        public List<org.apache.hadoop.fs.Path> getCommittedFiles()
        从接口复制的说明: StoreFlushContext
        Returns the newly committed files from the flush. Called only if commit returns true
        指定者:
        getCommittedFiles 在接口中 StoreFlushContext
        返回:

      • replayFlush

        public void replayFlush(List<String> fileNames,
                        boolean dropMemstoreSnapshot)
                 throws IOException
        Similar to commit, but called in secondary region replicas for replaying the flush cache from primary region. Adds the new files to the store, and drops the snapshot depending on dropMemstoreSnapshot argument.
        指定者:
        replayFlush 在接口中 StoreFlushContext
        参数:
        fileNames - names of the flushed files
        dropMemstoreSnapshot - whether to drop the prepared memstore snapshot
        抛出:
        IOException
